OL,3,CLegacy Funeral Directors: Families
OL,4,Cconsulted on permanent memorials
OL,6,FFamilies affected by a police
OL,7,Finvestigation into a Hull funeral home
OL,8,Fare being consulted on designs for a
OL,9,Fpermanent memorial.
OL,11,FIn March 2024, 35 bodies and a
OL,12,Fquantity of ashes were removed from
OL,13,Fthe premises of Legacy Funeral
OL,14,FDirectors when police received a
OL,15,Freport of concern for care for the
OL,16,Fdeceased.
OL,18,FHull City Council has announced that
OL,19,Ftwo memorial gardens are to be built,
OL,20,Fwhere the ashes of those involved can
OL,21,Fbe laid to rest.
