OL,6,FAn architect is designing spaces for
OL,7,FNorthern Cemetary in Hull and Lelley
OL,8,FFields Crematorium in the East Riding
OL,9,Fof Yorkshire.
OL,11,FTracy Meyerhoff, from the council,
OL,12,Fsaid: "We know that we are a year on
OL,13,Ffrom this incident emerging, and we're
OL,14,Fcontinuing to support people who are
OL,15,Fstill dealing with this distressing
OL,16,Fsituation.
