OL,6,F"It's really important that they are
OL,7,Finvolved in shaping these permanent
OL,8,Fmemorials, so we've been hearing from
OL,9,Fthem about the type of things they'd
OL,10,Flike to have."
OL,12,FFuneral directors investigation: What
OL,13,Fdo we know so far?
OL,15,FThe council said the main building
OL,16,Fwork is expected to be complete by
OL,17,Flate spring or early summer.
OL,19,FSeveral events are due to be held to
OL,20,Fshowcase the plans to the wider public.
